//Changelog

reward crates use item crate drops from sky open crate when empty disappear

1.3.0
- When a flare is used a firework is now fired up to the sky, after time the pinata spawns and drops, launch color is based on the color value in the pinata json file
- Added Stream codec for pinatas,
- Added client syncing for flares to show correctly in multiplayer
- Added new flare crate, this flare works similar to the pinata expect it spawns a crate that drops from the sky and opens on impact
- To add new crate create a json file in data/shops/crates like this
```js
{
  "loot_table": "minecraft:blocks/gravel",
}```
- Like Pinatas any loot table can be used here
- Networking applied to this crate flare as well

1.2.0
- Added buttons to shop the indicate that there is more items to buy
- Search box now resets the scroll index to prevent empty search results even when there are items to show
- JEI now shows all added flare items that are added via data packs
- Flare item now uses translations "item.shops.pinata_flare.TYPE" type is the path of the pinata json excluding the name space ig shops:mineshaft becomes item.shops.pinata_flare.mineshaft

1.1.1
- Updated logo
- Added new pinata textures
- Changed pinata loader to use a loot table instead of chance results
- Loader now looks like this;
```js
{
  "main_color": "#FF0000FF",
  "loot_table": "minecraft:blocks/gravel",
  "model": "shops:1"
}```
- Main color is used to tint the flare item used to spawn the pinata
- Loot table is used to get the items that will drop from the pinata
- model is used to select the texture for the pinata based on a horse model we have 1-10 thanks @Yuki for these textures
- Pinata flares now dynamically create there texture based on the main color in the loader file
- Flare now consumed on use
- Reduced shadow size
- Pinatas can no longer be sat on by players
- Pinatas now drop in the exact location the flare was used, with rotation looking at the player
- Pinatas now take between 3 to 7 hits to break into loot
- Loot now spawns at once
- This update contains a few example pinatas in data/shops/pinatas which will be removed in a future update

1.1.0
- Added Pinata's inside data/pinatas folder create a list of ChanceResults items after a reload there will be a flare item that is used to spawn the pinata
- Each hit on the pinata will drop the items inside the list in order until the last entry is completed
- Each pinata has a texture location that is used for the pinata model based on a horse the texture goes in assets/modid/textures/entity/pinatas/name_or_pinata.png
- This updated contains a few examples of pinatas

1.0.5
- Fixed reloading error when using /reload command

1.0.4
- Fixed custom data loading recipes not actually being on the client side, fixes missing recipes in JEI for selling and buying items
- Balance now saves after death
- Coins now added to balance every seconds instead of every tick to reduce impact on performance
- Coins when added to balance now play a sound effect

1.0.3
- Fixed JEI support to show buying and selling correctly
- Changed names to Player Buying and Player Selling in JEI to make it more clear

1.0.2
- Added loot table and pickaxe tag to shop
- Completely reworked shop json, now uses a single catalog item then each shop entry has a mode of buying or selling

```js
{
  "catalog": { "id": "minecraft:book" },
  "entries": [
    { "stack": { "id": "minecraft:paper", "count": 2 }, "price": 50, "mode": "player_buys" },
    { "stack": { "id": "minecraft:leather", "count": 1 }, "price": 200, "mode": "player_buys" },
    { "stack": { "id": "minecraft:diamond", "count": 1 }, "price": 250, "mode": "player_sells" }
  ]
}
```
- these now go into the data/modid/catalogs folder instead of the 2 old ones
- Right/Left Clicking on the auto produced item will now clear it
- Shop now scrolls if there are more than 12 entries to buy
- Added Auto Updating to curse forge

1.0.1
- Player balance command add, set and remove now require permission level 4
- Added player_balance transfer command to transfer from your balance to another player's balance